```plantuml
@startuml xydo1990_mlops_zoomcamp_homework

actor User
participant "Batch Prediction Service" as BatchService
participant "Stream Prediction Service" as StreamService
participant "Prefect Orchestrator" as Prefect
participant "MLflow Model Registry" as MLflow
participant "Evidently Monitoring" as Evidently
database "MongoDB" as MongoDB

User -> BatchService: Submit batch prediction request
BatchService -> MLflow: Fetch production model
MLflow --> BatchService: Return model
BatchService -> MongoDB: Load input data
MongoDB --> BatchService: Return data
BatchService -> BatchService: Perform predictions
BatchService -> Evidently: Log predictions for monitoring
Evidently --> BatchService: Acknowledge
BatchService --> User: Return predictions

User -> StreamService: Submit streaming prediction request
StreamService -> MLflow: Fetch production model
MLflow --> StreamService: Return model
StreamService -> StreamService: Process stream
StreamService -> Evidently: Continuously monitor predictions
Evidently --> StreamService: Acknowledge
StreamService --> User: Stream predictions

Prefect -> BatchService: Trigger scheduled batch prediction
BatchService -> MLflow: Fetch production model
MLflow --> BatchService: Return model
BatchService -> MongoDB: Load input data
MongoDB --> BatchService: Return data
BatchService -> BatchService: Perform predictions
BatchService -> Evidently: Log predictions for monitoring
Evidently --> BatchService: Acknowledge

@enduml
```